
=Bio=

"I am french, born in 84 passionnated about life. I studied business and travelled in Mexico & Argentina to see the world and the huge wealth inequities that are spreading more and more between the poor and the rich.

2009 I decided to go full time in order to create better systems and to discover what is inner abundance.

Today, I work in the complementary currency field, in order to fix money as we know it.

I advocate for a shared governance and a shared power in deciding what has value.
I speak, teach, write, consult on this topic.

I am based in Paris.

I've been writing on my blog since august 2009 my research about money, monetary mass, sharing economy, Abundance & Scarcity and how do we use the internet/digital to share more what doesn't cost us!"

